thread.title: Fresh tension in Noida

author: tribuneindia.com
title: Fresh tension in Noida
text:
Lucknow, October 5
Tension mounted in Gautam Buddha Nagar on Sunday night after the carcass of a cow was found in Dadri village, said IG (administration) Prakash D, here today. “On the complaint of Chithauda village gram pradhan, a case under section 302 of IPC has been lodged against unknown persons. The flesh has been sent for forensic test,” the IG said. In a related development, the UP Police asked Twitter India to delete a tweet from a twitter handle in Noida, on September 30, a day after an angry mob lynched a 55-year old ironsmith at Dadri village. — TNS
